{"tid":1319393,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一句影響警察戰意嘅說話","createTime":"2019-07-15T06:57:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T10:04:02.000Z","uid":98477,"like":244,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"d7f2d467d8386f433c9b244ff17597b0dfbeb330","tid":1319393,"uid":98477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:57:45.000Z","msg":"隔離po有人講，唔好再屌警察，因為佢地對粗口免疫，應該講說話影響士氣，令佢地懷疑人生。我非常同意佢嘅講法。<br />\n<br />\n所以我想喺度集思廣益，將呢啲種屌走警察嘅方法發揚光大。<br />\n<br />\n我睇到有一啲samples，覺得幾有效，歡迎接龍：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nxxx (地區名，最好夠精準) 唔需要你啊，你嚟呢度仲搞亂個場。你班廢物同我走，唔想見到你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n望住個鏡頭啊，俾你舊同學睇下你做狗個樣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你老婆會因為你份工而鐘意你？鐘意你份糧咋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f89bb6c56db251e5528893725d14c77c69900562","tid":1319393,"uid":6020,"like":129,"dislike":3,"score":126,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:59:53.000Z","msg":"你老婆而家同人3P緊啦警犬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"245c895a38ac1cea51d3dac5ec377875463af15f","tid":1319393,"uid":98477,"like":118,"dislike":3,"score":115,"quote":{"pid":"f89bb6c56db251e5528893725d14c77c69900562","tid":1319393,"uid":6020,"like":129,"dislike":3,"score":126,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:59:53.000Z","msg":"你老婆而家同人3P緊啦警犬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:02:44.000Z","msg":"我會講：<br />\n你個仔咁乖，邊忽似你？你個仔係咪你架？"},{"pid":"14cd4de34087288b7c639c220c4678271bf5fcd0","tid":1319393,"uid":32836,"like":9,"dislike":7,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:02:57.000Z","msg":"香港警察<br />\n成班垃圾"},{"pid":"6386bed4117130f1847ae4986cd45a5a46ceb0fe","tid":1319393,"uid":98477,"like":47,"dislik