:"ef4c7814d4b46927b3fd300c4ccc99a67a251639","tid":1319393,"uid":95102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:11:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">唔好意思阻你少少位<br />\n我打咗份聲明俾721嘅義士宣讀<br />\n希望各位巴打可以入嚟幫手改下</div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n=========================<br />\n<br />\n721衝之前應該要搵人開記者會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320570\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320570</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n=========================<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">721聲明</span></div><br />\n<br />\n我們一眾香港人謹此聲明，我們在6月9日及6月16日已經以和平、理性、非暴力的方式，進行和平遊行表達過我們的訴求但政府屢次漠視民意、又以前線警員作為擋箭牌，故此我們於2019年7月21日的一切行動都是以五大訴求為目的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求包括：<br />\n<br />\n1.要求政府確實地使用「撤回」的字眼<br />\n撤回《2019年逃犯及刑事事宜相互法律協助法例（修訂）條例草案》（即《逃犯條例》）<br />\n<br />\n2.撤回612暴動定性，警方於6月12日晚上發出的反對集會通知書，其中列明警方將當日「集會定性為暴動」故此我們要求政府撤回6月12日遊行示威的暴動定性。<br />\n<br />\n3.不檢控、釋放及撤回所有抗爭者控罪，連日以來的遊行示威中有多名示威者被警方拘捕，我們要求警方釋放「由6月9日至政府承諾此項訴求當日」的所有示威者，並且永不追究，包括但不限於以下兩項：<br />\n一、不以任何形式、任何罪名拘捕、控告任何示威者<br />\n二、確保所有示威者不被任何國家機構侵害人身自由以及財產利益<br />\n<br />\n4.追究警隊濫權，於連日以來的遊行示威中，警方多次未有展示委任證及警員編號包括 ：快速應變小隊（速龍小隊）， 雖然保安局局長李家超指該小隊制服未有足夠位置展示警員編號，但在2016年旺角警民衝突中其肩章仍縫有警員編號。<br />\n另外警方多次以過分武力驅趕示威者，包括在示威者後退時使用警棍、胡椒噴劑、 催淚彈等驅逐正在和平退去的示威者，又以警棍、胡椒噴劑襲擊穿上反光衣及已表明身份的記者，我們強烈譴責這些濫權的行為並且要求政府成立獨立調查委員會，追究濫用武力警員。<br />\n<br />\n5.落實雙普選，政府在連日以來的遊行示威多次漠視民意，甚至有與香港市民作對之嫌，所以問題根本在於香港政府本身，我們要求政府以行政命令解散立法會、立即實行香港人一人一票普選立法會議員及行政長官。<br />\n<br />\n鑑於政府現時一直拒絕回應示威者訴求， 令到事態惡化，警民關係繃緊， 加劇社會撕裂，我們促請政府正面回應五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n在政府達到五大訴求前我們不會罷休， 並且會以一切方法迫使政府達到我們的訴求，但只要政府能夠達到我們的訴求，一眾示威者可以回復正常生活，香港人民就可以回復安定的生活，社會撕裂就會暫停。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我們一眾香港人在此促請香港政府正面回應五大訴求。</span></div></span>"},{"pid":"5af45b5306278097754181d6544f724537cb4a02","tid":1319393,"uid":22155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a81244093eb95e48e74ff2b301d39b584cbbe12","tid":1319393,"uid":5384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:48:54.000Z","msg":"等做權鬥炮灰啦"},{"pid":"90838b87c13152ee77ebf60c0aeeaca753fd955e","tid":1319393,"uid":182195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:59:16.000Z","msg":"拎塊鏡對住佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b896c4e9068d44969e2e5161ee54cf9d7b39f43f","tid":1319393,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T19:06:33.000Z","msg":"你地有冇睇新聞架<br />\n沙蛇係差館屌柒完班手足再返房屌女呀<br />\n你呀頭分分鐘都係咁架咋<br />\n又有免費閪屌又有冷氣涼<br />\n你睇下你身水身汗咁做乜鳩<br />\n返去一齊百人斬條女喇傻閪"},{"pid":"e89c3779684c8e907c6f11e95b44cca0ae30399a","tid":1319393,"uid":174403,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"989324d4cd14cb8bf1c191d7ee445f76ae130750","tid":1319393,"uid":62710,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:46:14.000Z","msg":"上面講人老婆果d我覺得唔可取<br />\n只會激怒d警察<br />\n<br />\n重點應該係比佢地知道羞恥<br />\n比佢地知道唔係得服從指令一條路<br />\n<br />\n「係香港人就除低裝備企過黎市民呢邊！」<br />\n「你地仲想比班高層高官利用到幾時呀豬兜！佢地等緊你地出事比佢地攞民意咋！」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T19:47:00.000Z","msg":"咁多個回覆<br />\n你呢個可謂最膠最蠢<br />\n<br />\n睇得好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f7c213c05c9e83bad12403b50bf5c3af7edc9b","tid":1319393,"uid":98477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T10:35:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a33a80def444efb735f527443981dbe1b4cd5c64","tid":1319393,"uid":172826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:36:19.000Z","msg":"到你喇Alvin Sin冼彤霖警員 癬蛇好撚想紅 麻煩大家入幫幫佢<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/djEsNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/djEsNS</a>"},{"pid":"8d39d7b7d078226ff7a01e5872c3bf6614c4a1c1","tid":1319393,"uid":265731,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:40:11.000Z","msg":"你地老婆喺人地屋企happy緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848f0b0937fedb5d9be6e876f72b57eeb8100524","tid":1319393,"uid":98477,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:56:06.000Z","msg":"試下放工同人講你做警察吖，睇下啲人笑你毅進仔，定話你正義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n你試下著軍裝落茶記，睇下啲人點望住你？人地笑你龜咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n如果我係你，我就砍掉重練。但係你做過警察，職場無人要你架啦，你做步兵送pizza啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n唔好話我挑釁你啊。你落簿嘅話，我諗你連個釁字都未識寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n企直啲，俾啲精神，俾大家睇下你幾有型！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bac6f70a91cd2576b7d3fce73e0d576b30c4f28","tid":1319393,"uid":187109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:02:50.000Z","msg":"香港人唔需要你呀"},{"pid":"52dc6d9763c5d31acbe838950901401ab504cb7e","tid":1319393,"uid":98477,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:06:45.000Z","msg":"社會無人鐘意打打殺殺嘅人！<br />\n但係你除咗識喊打喊殺之外，仲識啲乜？<br />\n整水電三行工程你又無牌，學位你又無個，律師醫生你唔識字。<br />\n你成世人做過咩好事？<br />\n你做人做成咁，仲有咩價值同意義？<br />\n送外賣都唔要兇神惡煞啦。<br />\n社會無人要你啊。"},{"pid":"0c961c4bbb3773e3e8ac54693265c1783b253540","tid":1319393,"uid":98477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:13:49.000Z","msg":"你企喺度啦，因為你除咗企喺度之外，你嘅一舉一動對社會都係負累，浪費社會資源。無你喺度大家開開心心，你一嚟就大家想打人。你嘅存在只係個多餘。<br />\n努力啲，知唔知。你仲要幫白衫升職架。"},{"pid":"c056cd4a21bdce999e3c85af825516a442d8859c","tid":1319393,"uid":81008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:19:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e6ac6efa184e4b8fa6e0331fa2edc0ea883c1e","tid":1319393,"uid":98477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:44:32.000Z","msg":"警察多你一個唔多，少你一個唔少。<br />\n佢叫你上嚟，唔係睇得起你，而係貪你夠細粒，你犯錯係你揹曬，你死你事。如果上面班人唔識性，推你去死，你入咗浩園，冚旗嗰下過後，無人會再記得你。人地就個個升職。<br />\n你存在嘅意義就係墊底同俾人利用。<br />\n<br />\n成世人有咩成就？<br />\n幫坐寫字樓班人拎荷蘭水蓋，自己就企喺度曬？"},{"pid":"ff3890c209c9ad0bf9aea184660f16452b185cee","tid":1319393,"uid":98477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T01:35:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80e7b5eb2e7bf9c1334540e03fff3133ef19d0d7","tid":1319393,"uid":80834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:22:58.000Z","msg":"我唔會屌你老母因為我唔屌狗架"},{"pid":"370eaf6a87f9845090e58eec59ceb02bc784b631","tid":1319393,"uid":83602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:36:32.000Z","msg":"你屋企人知唔知你做差佬"},{"pid":"0aec189cffa8e0700b351c1bf5463138158676d1","tid":1319393,"uid":281584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:40:51.000Z","msg":"關二哥會唔會打鳩蜀國人呀<br />\n舉頭三尺有神明"},{"pid":"67582483b3ccd0972c689aae8e99f037c659b077","tid":1319393,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:42:46.000Z","msg":"喂師兄/姐，你髮型亂咗喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}